<item>
            <title>[LU-8382] HSM: reorder coordinator&apos;s cleanup functions</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8382</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The coordinator is initialized in mdt_handler.c&lt;br/&gt;
In mdt_init0() the functions mdt_hsm_cdt_init() and hsm_cdt_procfs_init() are called in that order.&lt;br/&gt;
In mdt_fini() the related cleanup functions: mdt_hsm_cdt_fini() and hsm_cdt_procfs_fini() are called in the same order.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
